snippet.title: The Sims 3 Katy Perry's Sweet Treats - First Look Trailer
snippet.description: Indulge your Sims' sweet tooth with The Sims™ 3 Katy Perry's Sweet Treats -- Available June 5, 2012! This pack showcases a vast range of décor items, furniture, and, of course, fabulous fashions and hairstyles, all inspired by Katy's real-life clothing and props, plus three new spectacular venues!
